com.thomasdiewald.ps3eye

Class PS3EyeP5

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thomasdiewald.ps3eye.PS3Eye
      • com.thomasdiewald.ps3eye.PS3EyeP5

  • public class PS3EyeP5
extends PS3Eye
    PS3Eye Camera for Processing Applications. It is only different to its super "PS3Eye" as it keeps a reference to the PApplet and a PImage as a framebuffer.
    Author:
    Thomas Diewald
